- Did they bring him out?
- Ambulance left two minutes ago.

29:36.375 --> 29:39.478
You're a lifetime too late. Nice camera!

29:43.949 --> 29:45.582
On to the next.

29:58.731 --> 30:01.200
I bet I wasted five dollars
