I promise you.

39:53.825 --> 39:56.728
"Bed, Bath & Beyond."

39:56.828 --> 39:58.861
Oh, that's a good store.

40:01.199 --> 40:04.836
Making peace with what you don't have,
that's what it's all about.

40:05.036 --> 40:09.174
Living with what you ain't got, right?
Don't you think?

40:09.274 --> 40:11.643
<i>Traffic units, ambulance traffic,
Benedict Canyon.</i>

40:11.743 --> 40:15.780
- <i>Overturned vehicle with injuries.</i>
- Crash with injuries. Good neighborhood.

40:19.784 --> 40:21.286
TV news. What happened?

40:21.386 --> 40:24.889
I think it was a head-on collision,
and there's a guy who's dead over there.

40:24.989 --> 40:26.491
- There's a woman...
- Did you see what happened?

40:26.591 --> 40:28.627
Am I supposed to help?
