into a picture but keeps it there longer,

43:06.785 --> 43:10.452
dissolving the barrier between the
subject and the outside of the frame.

43:11.623 --> 43:13.456
Is that blood on your shirt?

43:14.459 --> 43:16.595
I don't think so.

43:16.995 --> 43:20.966
I recently heard of a Mexican restaurant
called Cabanita. Have you heard of it?

43:21.066 --> 43:22.999
It's also on your sleeve.

43:24.435 --> 43:26.402
I didn't see that.

43:28.673 --> 43:31.574
What I'm asking is,
do you like Mexican food, Nina?

43:32.544 --> 43:33.612
Yes.

43:33.712 --> 43:36.414
Stand by, people. Here we go.

43:36.514 --> 43:40.148
Cabanita has been called
"an authentic taste of Mexico City."

43:42.754 --> 43:45.721
Do you wanna go with me?
I think we could have fun together.

43:46.357 --> 43:49.094
- Thanks, but I'm busy.
- Saturday is your night off, isn't it?

43:49.194 --> 43:53.264
I have a rule, Lou.
I don't date people I work with.

43:53.464 --> 43:56.499
- And I'm twice your age.
- I like older women.

43:57.202 --> 43:59.671
Besides, I don't work with you.
You're someone I sell to.

43:59.771 --> 44:02.273
And I don't wanna fuck that up.

44:02.373 --> 44:04.610
What if by saying no, you fuck it up?

44:05.210 --> 44:06.711
All right, 10 seconds to go and back on.

44:06.811 --> 44:08.377
Is that what you're saying?

44:10.215 --> 44:13.548
- I didn't say that.
- Eight, seven...

44:13.648 --> 44:16.521
- ...six, five, four...
- Well, I don't know what to say.

44:16.621 --> 44:18.957
...three, two, one.

44:19.057 --> 44:21.092
Good morning. Thank you
for joining us. I'm Lisa Mays.

44:21.192 --> 44:24.496
