44:28.934 --> 44:31.000
Severely injured a young woman.

44:32.871 --> 44:34.523
Hey, Lou!

44:36.107 --> 44:38.877
Hey, man. Joe Loder, Mayhem.

44:38.977 --> 44:43.148
Great get tonight. They were closing
it down by the time we showed up.

44:43.248 --> 44:45.216
