45:22.921 --> 45:26.090
- You like the Canon 305s?
- Never used one.

45:26.190 --> 45:31.797
Six thou a piece. 2.4 megapixels.
Night vision. 18:1 zoom.

45:32.197 --> 45:34.499
I got one of those puppies
with your name on it.

45:34.599 --> 45:35.900
I have a camera.

45:36.000 --> 45:40.205
I want you running my second van.
Two crews. Half the area to cover.

45:40.305 --> 45:43.041
Now, I know what you're thinking.
Half the money, right?

45:43.141 --> 45:45.110
You should be thinking, twice the sales.

45:45.210 --> 45:47.746
Because we're going to be
the first at every scene.

45:47.846 --> 45:50.014
Why compete when we can work together?

45:50.114 --> 45:54.018
You can share my press cards.
Puppy dog off my police connections.

45:54.118 --> 45:57.823
This is the big move, the next level.
